-- Ferrari May Open Russian Subsidiary, Vedomosti Reports
-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 2012-05-23T05:32:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-23/ferrari-may-open-russian-subsidiary-vedomosti-reports.html
Luca Cordero di Montezemolo, chairman
of Ferrari SpA, said he is considering opening a subsidiary in
 Russia  to boost sales in the country,  Vedomosti  said, citing an
interview with him.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow at 
